item.title: Almond and Cashew Healthy Balls
item.description: Ingredients 150g cashews 150g almonds 40g shredded coconut 200g dried figs, roughly chopped 3tsp maca powder 3tbl cacao powder 2tbl white sesame seeds 30g agave syrup 50g coconut oil, melted Method Add cashews, almonds & coconut to TM bowl.
